strapiSongs.title: Trip-tamine
strapiSongs.lyrics:
Dr. Timothy Leary:
*They came to Socrates and said*
*Stop saying that Socrates*
*You’re corrupting the mind of youth*

*There is no self*
*There is no knowledge*
*Obey*
*Believe*

*Socrates would not be stopped*
*He said know thyself*
*Operate your brain*
strapiSongs.credits:
• Music by Victor Fisher
• Video by Dr. Timothy Leary
strapiSongs.description:
A psychedelic soundtrack for an epic video by Dr. Timothy Leary.

*Socrates said know thyself*
